rows.label: qst002206_msg0001
rows.name: Um... how did the investigation go?

rows.label: qst002206_msg0002
rows.name:
There was a girl who tried to join the
Choir at the same time as me, and she's
an Invidian from the refugee camp...

rows.label: qst002206_msg0007
rows.name:
There was only one spot available
in the Choir last time... I'm sure
it's because I was accepted...

rows.label: qst002206_msg0008
rows.name:
Um, could you come with me? I'd
like to try and meet Albina-san...

rows.label: qst002206_msg0009
rows.name:
N-no, it's alright, I can go. I'll
feel safe if you're with me...

rows.label: qst002206_msg0010
rows.name:
I want to talk to her
properly. Let's go...
